	<version>0.1.0.1</version>
	<title>Tardis Teleport</title>
	<description>
		<en><![CDATA[
This is a revamp of the good old Tardis from FS17.

For beginners: With Tardis you can teleport yourself or your vehicles to any location on the map.
Besides that it has a couple of additional functionality. See below.

More Details: https://github.com/sperrgebiet/FS19_Tardis

Kudos to Ifko[nator] for the RegisterSpecialization script.
]]>
		</en>
		<de><![CDATA[
Dies ist eine Reinkarnation von Tardis aus LS17
Für Neueinsteiger: Mit Tardis kannst du dich selbst oder eines deiner Fahrzeuge zu jeder Lokation teleportieren.

Mehr Details: https://github.com/sperrgebiet/FS19_Tardis

Kudos to Ifko[nator] for the RegisterSpecialization script.
]]>
		</de>
		<it>
			<![CDATA[
			Questo è un rinnovamento del buon vecchio Tardis di FS17.

			Per i principianti: con Tardis puoi teletrasportare te stesso o i tuoi veicoli in qualsiasi posizione sulla mappa.
			Oltre a ciò ha un paio di funzionalità aggiuntive. Vedi sotto.

			Maggiori dettagli: https://github.com/sperrgebiet/FS19_Tardis

			Complimenti a Ifko[nator] per lo script RegisterSpecialization.
			]]>
		</it>
	</description>
	<iconFilename>icon.dds</iconFilename>
	<multiplayer supported="true" />

	<extraSourceFiles>
		<sourceFile filename="RegisterSpecialization.lua" />
	</extraSourceFiles>	
	
	<registerSpecializations debugPriority="0">
		<registerSpecialization name="tardis" className="Tardis" filename="Tardis.lua" searchedSpecializations="Enterable"/>
	</registerSpecializations>	


	<actions>
		<action name="tardis_showTardisCursor" axisType="HALF" />
		<action name="tardis_resetVehicle" axisType="HALF" />
		<action name="tardis_useHotspot1" axisType="HALF" />
		<action name="tardis_useHotspot2" axisType="HALF" />
		<action name="tardis_useHotspot3" axisType="HALF" />
		<action name="tardis_useHotspot4" axisType="HALF" />
